## MSICStake class

Represents a user's MSIC stake and accrued gains.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare class MSICStake 
```

## Remarks

Returned by the [getMSICStake()](./lib-base.readablemosaic.getmsicstake.md) function.

The constructor for this class is marked as internal. Third-party code should not call the constructor directly or create subclasses that extend the `MSICStake` class.
